tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
review:
**** ** *** ******** **** * **** **** *** ** ** ***** Over all experience is horrible front the time I have arrived. 
1. I made a pre booking appointment at 6 30pm and reached there at 6 30pm and informed the receptionist and they told me to wait for 30 minutes. And I go back to check on the status and to my surprise they ask me what is the issue and what you have come for. Wonderful treatment they gave. 

2. After patiently explaining them the situation, 5 mins later the lady comes and asks me for an ID proof for patient and without it we cannot proceed further. Which we never carry everyday to prove our identity to everyone and nothing was mentioned during appointment call. And I told them after I reach home would send the details. 

3. This time I approach this * * * * * * * * **** doctor DHARANI just to clarify one of the doubts I had and she IS NOT READY TO LISTEN AND CLARIFY MY DOUBT and shuts the door on my face with my wife inside who has communication barrier despite my wife telling her the same. And in the end she gives me some report which I didn't understand and have been trying to ask that Lady for the same and she starts yelling on me insulting me and my wife telling me "why should I explain it you" One wonderful answer from a Doctor DHARANI. I did not utter a bad word at her considering her old age and she calls me S T U P I D in the end. And all these happened there from 6 30 pm to close to 9pm and doesn't let me out without paying which is want they wanted.  

4. In the end I ask what's the point of booking an appointment and she says that is how they function. ******** **** ** *** **** ** ******* Strongly recommend DO NOT GO TO THIS PLACE. **** ** *** *** **** ***** ** ***** *** *** **** ***** ****** ****

review:
Hi my name is sindu and i consulted with Dr. Dharani Bai mam having stomach pain during my cycle and she did my pelvic scan and detected that i had multiple fibroids and it was in the stage where it was calcified and needed an emergency surgery. If I had not meet Dr. Dharani Bai mam i might have been gone to a stage of hysterectomy without giving birth to a baby. I am really thankful to Dr. Dharani Bai mam from my bottom of my heart and I highly recommend Dr. Dharani Bai mam for all who are suffering from any gynec or obstractic problem, 
and they can consult Dr. Dharani Bai. She is really a super caring doctor.

We have visited the hospital and met the doctor for my mother-in-law. Consultation was fine with the doctor. I knew doctor for the last 12 years and she is very good, approachable and friendly. I have already recommended doctor to my family or friends. Even she did my delivery past 10 years. One of my friend referred long back. Doctor told me to avoid tablets, she motivates me a lot. She told me to do physical exercise. We had been for a second opinion with the doctor. There was not much waiting time in the hospital, it was for 20 minutes. Diet was suggested.

I had met the doctor. ********* *** **** ** ******* Whatever problem I had she listened to everything and she was good. I am satisfied with explanation and treatment given by doctor.  I would like to recommend this doctor to my family and friends. My friend recommended me this doctor initially. Tablets were prescribed by the doctor. Scanning was done. There was no waiting time in the hospital. Visited for gyneac issue and later issue got resolved. She told me to avoid outside food, junk food as I had PCOD symptoms and told me how to cope up with it.

My wife had consulted the doctor and it was for health concern. Consultation experience was good with the doctor. I would like to recommend this doctor to my family and friends. I am satisfied with the explanation given. There was more waiting time in the hospital, its more than 30 minutes. Doctor was not able to give time to patients and turn around time is more. Time management and manpower should be proper and that is the only drawback. Medicine was prescribed by the doctor. Medical tests was done. Doctor was friendly during the consultation.

context: Pregnancy Scan,Pregnancy,Normal Vaginal Delivery (NVD),Obstetrics Problems,Pregnancy Check Up,
review: We have consulted Dr. Dharani Bai G throughout the pregnancy, delivering Normal, Full Term, Healthy Baby and providing a strength to the mother.We reached out first time to her for planning of first pregnancy at earlier stage. She analyzed all health concerns in detail for both of us and provided appropriate treatment to conceive a baby in hardly second cycle of our visit. Her expertise in identifying different risk parameters in the lab reports, ultrasound and anomaly scan really helped us to cure problems at the earlier stage to avoid later complications.She never asked us to do any unnecessary tests or scans and always focused on health and safety of mother availing virtually or in person at Cloudnine.She advised my wife to get admission at hospital at the right time for the term delivery around 40 weeks and consistently stayed in touch at mid-night along with Cloudnine on-duty doctors to monitor mother and fetus health. She was present in person in the early morning for ensuring normal delivery and had encouraged mother during labour pain.I definitely recommend Dr. Dharani Bai G to all those couples who want a solid expertise, polite and attentive Obstetrics/Gynacologist doctor to be there as a mother at Cloudnine Whitefield.Thanks Dr. Dharani Bai G madam for gifting us a healthy baby with lifetime experience of happiness.
